693
00:52:57,679 --> 00:52:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] Žele samo da bude.

694
00:52:58,400 --> 00:52:59,760
[SPEAKER_01] To je i demotivirajuće.

695
00:53:00,239 --> 00:53:00,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

696
00:53:00,719 --> 00:53:02,079
